Host Discovery
//Cain uses ARP scanner for host discovery
Start Sniffer Component > Sniffer Tab > Hosts Subtab > Right-click Scan MAC addresses

ARP Poisoning
Sniffer Component > APR > + > Hijack traffic between Target and it's gateway. 
Intercepted HTTP and FTP creds should be in the Passwords tab within the Sniffer component.

Cracking
Cracker tab > LM&NTLM Hashes > Right-click Add to List.
